00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:08,220
However,

305
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:10,100
let me tell you.

306
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:11,620
The society university is complex.

307
00:13:11,900 --> 00:13:12,780
For example,

308
00:13:12,780 --> 00:13:13,900
your officialdom

309
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:15,980
