368
00:14:54,510 --> 00:14:55,820
- Don't meddle.
- Mother.

369
00:14:57,980 --> 00:14:59,100
Let's start from this side.

370
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:00,500
- He can't play.
- Father.

371
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:18,700
Your Highness.

372
00:15:24,820 --> 00:15:25,660
Anran,

373
00:15:26,260 --> 00:15:27,660
your family is a noble family.

374
00:15:28,300 --> 00:15:30,460
How could you be engaged
to a merchant's girl?

375
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:33,340
This family

376
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:35,660
seems quite strange.

377
00:15:37,530 --> 00:15:38,660
I've also been puzzled.

378
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:41,220
But my parents never cared
about family background,

379
00:15:41,490 --> 00:15:42,620
so it's not strange.

380
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:44,500
As you can see,

381
00:15:44,500 --> 00:15:46,540
the Shens are not deceitful.

382
00:15:47,620 --> 00:15:48,700
These days,

383
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:49,900
they've treated me sincerely

384
00:15:50,060 --> 00:15:51,100
without any unusual moves.

385
00:15:52,780 --> 00:15:54,940
Have you checked their background
in Qingyang?

386
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:56,620
Nothing

387
00:15:57,180 --> 00:15:58,260
is wrong with them.

388
00:16:01,860 --> 00:16:03,020
You didn't go?

389
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:05,660
To protect this family,

390
00:16:06,660 --> 00:16:08,340
you lied to me.

391
00:16:11,380 --> 00:16:12,660
I'm just worried

392
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:14,980
that investigating an old case
in Qingyang

393
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:16,780
might cause unnecessary trouble.

394
00:16:24,860 --> 00:16:26,940
Since you're planning
to overturn the Cui Case,

395
00:16:28,060 --> 00:16:30,180
why fear unnecessary trouble?

396
00:16:34,260 --> 00:16:36,300
Do you know how big a deal this is?

397
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:39,060
I took a risk to save you,

398
00:16:39,460 --> 00:16:41,300
not to let you be trapped in danger.

399
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:44,220
How do you know?

400
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:46,260
I was the one who raised you.

401
00:16:46,420 --> 00:16:47,540
Can't I see

402
00:16:48,700 --> 00:16:50,500
through your thoughts?

403
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:54,780
I know

404
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:57,620
