572
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:29,440
I told you to take care of him,

573
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:30,720
not to invite him.

574
00:23:32,780 --> 00:23:34,540
Mom, why didn't you stop him?

575
00:23:34,820 --> 00:23:36,160
What have I done wrong this time?

576
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:38,580
Your dad insisted on inviting him.

577
00:23:39,300 --> 00:23:40,180
I thought

